<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien sapna ka ngatsan dem?
 Leisiet guolnuom ka chen zing dem?
 Hinkhuo phat beih zung zung lai hin,
 Ka tha ipmu'n a um zing dem?

[V2]
 A hun sam hi, ngaiin (2)
 Pathien in nang A hun sam zing hi, Aw ngaiin;
 A hun sam hi, ngaiin (2)
 Pathien in nang A hun sam hi, Aw ngaiin.

[V3]
 2. Ei sam zing hi, ka kipan dem?
 Hehpih Aw nem limsak loin;
 Ei venna ka mawk umsak dem?
 Ei sam zing hi, ka ngakzing dem?

[V4]
 3. Ei sam zinga, A kiu zing hi,
 Ka lunggil kawt ka khak zing dem?
 Ei lawp dingin ei ngak zing hi,
 A Tha ka hih lungkham zing dem?

[V5]
 4. Ei sam zing hi, kawltang zingin,
 Ei sap limsak lo ding ka him?
 Ka ngaka, ei nungsawn ngei puoi,
 Ei sam hi, ka lunggil, halh in!

[V6]
 5. Ei sam zing hi, muong thei puong ka,
 Vaigei loin lunggil pieng ka;
 Khawvel, mangpha, hun nusieng ka,
 Pathien aw'n ka lung a thawng tai.</lyrics>
<title>GOD IS CALLING YET</title>
<hymn_number>200</hymn_number>
</song>